fd4a710a35ee/194f1a3bebbc1f7996398153ae126cdf/image.png?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimage.png&a=w%3D256%26h%3D192%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D70&cd=2020-05-03T09%3A33%3A59\",\"srcSet\":\"/_gatsby/image/047bec5e9159d735c0e6fd4a710a35ee/194f1a3bebbc1f7996398153ae126cdf/image.png?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimage.png&a=w%3D256%26h%3D192%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D70&cd=2020-05-03T09%3A33%3A59 256w,/_gatsby/image/047bec5e9159d735c0e6fd4a710a35ee/ed8fda1df1e24141b4dcea76246b223f/image.png?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimage.png&a=w%3D512%26h%3D384%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D70&cd=2020-05-03T09%3A33%3A59 512w,/_gatsby/image/047bec5e9159d735c0e6fd4a710a35ee/1f3b4c0d4b75f476e0dfc0884122d04c/image.png?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimage.png&a=w%3D1024%26h%3D768%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D70&cd=2020-05-03T09%3A33%3A59 1024w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":768},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\"wp-image-2396 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"2\"}</script><figcaption>Zoomでバーチャル背景を設定しているところ。背景が南国になっています。</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>以下に、バーチャル背景ができるWeb会議をまとめました。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Web会議アプリ</td><td>バーチャル背景</td><td>備考</td></tr><tr><td>Zoom</td><td>○</td><td>好きな背景画像を追加可能。</td></tr><tr><td>Microsoft Teams</td><td>一部○</td><td>インストール版のみバーチャル背景設定可能。<br>Web版はできない。</td></tr><tr><td>LINE</td><td>一部○</td><td>モバイル版のみバーチャル背景設定可能。<br>PC版はできない。</td></tr><tr><td>Skype</td><td>△</td><td>背景設定はできず、背景ぼかしができる。</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">終わりに</h1>\n\n\n\n<p>ひとえにテレワークといっても、単に働く場所が変わっただけという単純なものではなく、やってみると色々と細かなところで違いややりにくさを感じます。ただ、通勤しなくて良いなどの便利なところもあります。<br>今回ご紹介したものなども踏まえて、やりやすい形に工夫しながらテレワークをしていけると良いのかなと思います。</p>\n","excerpt":"<p>2020年、世間を騒がせている新型コロナウイルス。外出自粛が求められる中、職場が急遽テレワークを求めるケースも多々あると思います。私もそうした者の一人ですが、テレワーク経験の長い人から聞いたことも含めて、テレワークをする [&hellip;]</p>\n","slug":"telework","date":"2020/05/03","modified":"2024/06/09","featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"","gatsbyImage":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/25aa5c1c6eb6b5a2cd7134094803f431/telework.avif?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D57%26h%3D40%26fm%3Davif%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 57w,/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/12d8ab8b6873122eedf778e2861a815a/telework.avif?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D113%26h%3D80%26fm%3Davif%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 113w,/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/3034e3f06bead4eab3f45c9563f13108/telework.avif?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D226%26h%3D160%26fm%3Davif%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 226w,/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/6d431e84d06051a30713516fe133a257/telework.avif?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D452%26h%3D319%26fm%3Davif%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 452w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 226px) 226px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/1ed91bf0793102625f26bf98addf5093/telework.webp?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D57%26h%3D40%26fm%3Dwebp%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 57w,/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/604869d18f1dbb6ddf92d4066d581d17/telework.webp?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D113%26h%3D80%26fm%3Dwebp%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a043879ac821f2971cf 113w,/_gatsby/image/8aaa3b322d79c739d8b12ed9ebe88d67/f0f587541011a118596b480fe0cd3522/telework.webp?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Ftelework.jpg&a=w%3D226%26h%3D160%26fm%3Dwebp%26q%3D75&cd=0a7b6131e7ce2a